          { "name": "posted_date", "selector": "[data-automation-id='postedOn'] dd, dd:last-of-type", "type": "String" }
        ],
        "identityFields": ["title"],
        "_notes": "Workday SPA (wd103). URL includes search query to bias toward science roles — Workday ignores location URL params, so geographic filtering is handled by profile target_locations rules. Selectors use data-automation-id attributes (stable across Workday versions). Increased timeout and wait for SPA hydration. Added posted_date field and secondary item selector for variant Workday layouts."
      }
    },
